---
import '../styles/global.css' 
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Practice Set</title>
	</head>
	<body>
	<header class="text-5xl font-extrabold p-6 bg-emerald-700 text-white">Practice Set - Image Gallery</header>	
	<section class="max-w-5xl p-6">
		<p class="text-lg pl-10 mt-2">This is a practice set for an image gallery using Astro and Tailwind CSS. The images are received from <a href="https://picsum.photos">Picsum Photos</a>. The current gallery features 3 images. Students are tasked with completing this gallery by adding 6 more images and styling them appropriately.</p>
		<p class="text-lg pl-10 mt-4"> Styling for the gallery is handled through Tailwind CSS and the overall design can be determined by the student. Create something unique and visually appealing. The current setup is to get you started, but have fun and play around with what looks nice to you. All images should be responsive and scale appropriately on different screen sizes. All images <strong>must</strong> open to a new tab when clicked, diplasying the image in full-size.</p>
		</section>
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold pl-10 text-emerald-700">Image Gallery</h1>
	<div
      id="gallery"
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-10"
    >

      <!-- Image Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
      <a
  		href="https://picsum.photos/id/1015/1200/800"
  		target="_blank">
  	<img
    src="https://picsum.photos/id/1015/400/300"
    alt="Mountain landscape"
    class="w-full h-auto cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition"/>
		</a>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Mountain Landscape
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
	  <!-- Image Card 2 -->
	<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <a
		  href="https://picsum.photos/id/1025/1200/800"
		  target="_blank">
		<img
          src="https://picsum.photos/id/1025/400/300"
          data-full="https://picsum.photos/id/1025/1200/800"
          alt="Dog portrait"
          class="gallery-image w-full h-auto cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition"
        />
		</a>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Dog Portrait
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

	<!-- Image Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <a
		  href="https://picsum.photos/id/1035/1200/800"
		  target="_blank">
		<img
          src="https://picsum.photos/id/1035/400/300"
          data-full="https://picsum.photos/id/1035/1200/800"
          alt="Forest path"
          class="gallery-image w-full h-auto cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition"
        />
		</a>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Waterfall
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

	<!-- Add additional image cards below -->
<footer class="w-full text-emerald-700 text-center">
  <p class="p-6 text-left">This practice set example is created as part of the <strong>Graduate Credit Assignment</strong>.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
